  ('7a6eaa16-ddf8-994e-ffdd-599d2ec3d8bc', '7681fa27-38bd-e56b-fa36-6a2bb17edb46', 'Shamblerot Vectorium', 'Numberless Horde: In your Command phase in each of the following battle rounds, depending on your chosen battle size, add a new ^^**Poxwalkers**^^ unit with a Starting Strength of 10 to your army, in Strategic Reserves.
