  ('2a7c6cc2-72eb-3f18-8b48-4862882ea8ae', 'dd2936a0-6cc2-791b-ad34-8323b51b6e9d', 'Khorne Daemonkin', 'Blood Tithe: Each time a ^^**Blood Legions^^** or ^^**World Eaters^^** unit from your army destroys an enemy unit, roll one D6; on a 3+, you gain 1 Blood Tithe point (BTP). At the start of the Command phase, you can spend 1 or more of your BTP to activate one of the following abilities until the end of the battle.
