  ('821c11ee-a654-9ec2-77a7-ad24a3dbc871', '1489fd95-e0fd-fa01-f54f-579693aeb35c', 'Profane Altar', 20, 'Each time the bearer makes a Dark Sacrifice, the maximum number of models are destroyed in the selected DAMNED unit (i.e. 3 if the unit’s Leadership test is passed, or 6 if it is failed) but, until the end of the phase, the bearer’s weapons have both [LETHAL HITS] and [SUSTAINED HITS 1].');
