  ('5f1d875d-1a1e-fc26-c090-9cb3ca853123', '357221af-141b-36a7-ab64-362195f7af89', 'Warp-borne Stalker', 25, 'The bearer has the Deep Strike ability. In addition, once per battle, at the end of your opponent''s turn, if the bearer is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, you can remove it from the battlefield and place it into Strategic Reserves.');
