  ('501f6c85-7d1b-6f21-5a90-48360a0340a1', '12815019-3087-b37b-aed6-e8ca893d7d00', 'Stone of Eldritch Fury', 15, 'Asuryani Psyker model only. Add 12" to the Range characteristic of ranged Psychic weapons equipped by the bearer.');
