  ('4167fd93-573d-1f8c-7419-57f90d930ba5', '485f89b8-3530-2805-7fbb-d258f261802b', 'Covenite Coterie', 'Stitchflesh Abominations: Each time an attack targets a **^^Haemonculus Covens^^** unit from your army, if the Strength characteristic of that attack is greater than the Toughness characteristic of your unit, subtract 1 from the Wound roll.')
