  ('09ffdc39-8a46-028f-afc7-ee47d97912fd', '26318249-8cb6-23b1-08f7-07ddeff63bea', 'Chrono-impedance Fields', 25, 'In your Command phase, select one friendly **^^Necrons Vehicle^^** or **^^Necrons Mounted^^** unit (excluding Titanic units) within 6" of the bearer. Until the start of your next Command phase, each time an attack is allocated to a model in that unit, subtract 1 from the Damage characteristic of that attack.');
