  ('5d23e478-a89c-3e89-ee4e-9458307c68a6', '6ac301cb-f812-bda3-64e9-f5985e814ab5', 'Glory Hog', 30, '**^^Beastboss On Squigosaur^^** model only. Models in the bearer''s unit have the Scouts 9" ability.');
